N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 17.6 - Number plates not continued

State Regulations

Number plates, which have the month and year of expiration
embossed thereon, shall not be continued for succeeding registration periods. Such number plates shall expire at the end of the month of the year which is
embossed thereon. Notes
